         <abstract>
            <p>Asymptotic expressions are derived for the singular value decomposition of a matrix some of whose columns approach zero. Expressions are also derived for the QR factorization of a matrix some of whose rows approach zero. The expressions give insight into the method of weights for approximating the solutions of constrained least squares problems.</p>
          </abstract>
